<Document>
  <name>Fort Bend County — Unmapped Historical Markers</name>
  <description>THC markers in Fort Bend County without an HMDB id (isMissing excluded). 8 with THC coords; 0 geocoded from address; 4 omitted (no usable address).</description>
  <Placemark>
    <name>[PENDING] Bullhead Convict Labor Camp Cemetery (HTC)</name>
